Wainwright. J. Chem. Phys. - 1954. - v. 22. - P. 881.</span></p>

<p class=Normal style='margin-left:14.15pt;text-indent:-14.15pt;line-height:
normal'>2. <span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:12.0pt'>И.И. Собельман. Введение в теорию атомных спектров.
М.: ГИФМЛ. - 1963. - С. 463 - 469.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-indent:14.2pt'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;text-indent:14.2pt'><span
